info.author: Rodrigo Palacios
info.description:
===============================
gitblog
===============================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/rodricios/gitblog.svg
        :target: https://travis-ci.org/rodricios/gitblog

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/gitblog.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/gitblog


Because you've always wanted to blog from a command prompt and/or Python script... Right?

* Free software: BSD license
* Documentation: https://gitblog.readthedocs.org.

Features
--------

* Pseudo-blogging capabilities brought to a Python shell near you!

* Already have a <username>.github.io page? Awesome! You can get started right away!

* Don't have a <username>.github.io page? Great! You can get started right away!




History
-------

0.0.1 (2015-03-15)
---------------------

* First release on PyPI.
